dataIdInfo.idPurp: Coordinates for Permafrost Monitoring sites provided by Bill Cable.
dataIdInfo.idAbs: Coordinates mark where permafrost monitoring instrumentation has been installed. Instruments are installed in the top left corner of each the intensive station. Coordinates are for proposed installation locatoins, not actual measured GPS points.
dataIdInfo.idCredit: Bill Cable and Vladimir Romanovsky for installation of permafrost monitoring stations and collecting GPS coordinates.
